00:05:52.860 --> 00:05:58.740
and the old index that Svelte has been replaced&nbsp;
by +page.svelte this new convention ensures&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:58.740 --> 00:06:03.420
that you are deliberately creating a route and&nbsp;
eliminates the need for the old naming convention&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:03.420 --> 00:06:08.640
that required you to use underscores in order to&nbsp;
