00:06:24.660 --> 00:06:30.900
directory using named layouts such as index at&nbsp;
about.svelte which we have since said goodbye to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:30.900 --> 00:06:36.180
in addition to these changes a new grouped layouts&nbsp;
convention was added and this allows us to share&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:36.180 --> 00:06:41.640
layouts within group directories which are folders&nbsp;
wrapped in parentheses group directories do not&nbsp;

00:06:41.640 --> 00:06:47.640
